"title": "8676: thanksgiving",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8676: thanksgiving",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The offering of thanks, especially for gifts received. Scripture emphasises the importance of giving thanks to God for all his gifts and works, both as an expression of our dependence upon him and gratitude to him.</p>\n<h2>Thanksgiving is sometimes linked with praise to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:30\">PSA 69:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:4\">1CH 16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:4\">PSA 42:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:4\">PSA 100:4</a></p>\n<h2>The duty of thanksgiving to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:3-1Tim4:4\">1TI 4:3–4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:8-Ps107:9\">PSA 107:8–107:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:7-Ps147:9\">PSA 147:7–147:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:17-Luke17:18\">LUK 17:17–17:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20-Rom1:21\">ROM 1:20–1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:6\">ROM 14:6</a></p>\n<h2>The expression of thanksgiving to God</h2>\n<h3>Through OT offerings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:14\">PSA 50:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:12-Lev7:15\">LEV 7:12–7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:9\">JON 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>In Christian gatherings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:16\">1CO 10:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:30\">1CO 10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:16-1Cor14:17\">1CO 14:16–14:17</a></p>\n<h3>Through song</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:2\">PSA 95:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:7-1Chr16:9\">1CH 16:7–16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:11\">EZR 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:8\">NEH 12:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:24\">NEH 12:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:27\">NEH 12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:46\">NEH 12:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:7\">PSA 147:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:3\">ISA 51:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:19\">JER 30:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:19-Eph5:20\">EPH 5:19–5:20</a></p>\n<h3>Through prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:1\">1TI 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh11:17\">NEH 11:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:10\">DAN 6:10</a></p>\n<h3>Through giving</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:11-2Cor9:12\">2CO 9:11–9:12</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In conversation</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:4\">EPH 5:4</a></p>\n<h2>Believers are to give thanks in all circumstances</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:18\">1TH 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6\">PHP 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:17\">COL 3:17</a></p>\n<h2>Thanksgiving for the blessings of salvation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:57\">1CO 15:57</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:24-Rom7:25\">ROM 7:24–7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:14\">2CO 2:14</a> <em>for victory through Christ</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:15\">2CO 4:15</a> <em>for God's grace</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:15\">2CO 9:15</a> <em>for Jesus Christ himself</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12\">COL 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:6-Col2:7\">COL 2:6–2:7</a> <em>for union with Christ</em></p>\n<h2>Examples of those who gave thanks to God</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:19\">MAT 14:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:16\">LUK 9:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:6\">MRK 8:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:30\">LUK 24:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:24\">1CO 11:24</a></p>\n<h3>Paul</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:15\">ACT 28:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:17\">ROM 6:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:16\">EPH 1:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:12\">1TI 1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Heavenly beings</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:9\">REV 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:12\">REV 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:17\">REV 11:17</a></p>",
